name: Aye Mya Phyu
description: '''Aye Mya Phyu''' ({{langx|my|အေးမြဖြူ}}; born 9 March 2003), also known as '''Moe Tho''' ({{lang|my|မိုးသို}}), is a Burmese singer, actress and former child star. She became famous after competing in the [[Myanmar Idol (season 4)|fourth season]] of ''[[Myanmar Idol]]'' and finishing as runner-up.
